{"tid":1703572,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"爆TVB黑幕被停工一年","createTime":"2019-11-10T10:44:04.000Z","updateTime":"2019-11-10T11:01:56.000Z","uid":297241,"like":5,"dislike":5,"uniUserReply":12,"replies":[{"pid":"073612140c38a520aca6968afcc910fcbb3414a4","tid":1703572,"uid":297241,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-10T10:44:04.000Z","msg":"爆TVB選美黑幕停工一年 <br />\n工藤佑采幫朋友做生意維生<br />\n<br />\n18年落選港姐工藤佑采（Yutori）及黎紀君（Christy）錄影《晚吹-學生妹．吹水班》，Yutori直認選美後已停工一年，有幫朋友做生意維持生計，目前自由身接洽活動，亦有意再簽經理人。問到TVB有否斟洽她？曾在社交網站怒爆TVB選美黑幕的她，即變得避忌說：「不方便說，他們（指TVB）未必喜歡我談論這話題。」<br />\n<br />\n談到曾與黃心穎爆罵戰，更怒斥對方扮乖乖女，因而被網友奉若「先知」，Yutori說：「好難回應喎！（你睇人好準？）不覺得，有時準有時不準。（認識心穎時已知她的行為？）她的個人行為與我無關，今次她不是話我，所以不評論了。」"},{"pid":"52406be781b8cbee8aae53476536b32df76f3144","tid":1703572,"uid":161105,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-11-10T10:48:54.000Z","msg":"條友屌示威者<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c628ce78f1598ffdd96d7f9b1507079a53759e77","tid":1703572,"uid":113929,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"52406be781b8cbee8aae53476536b32df76f3144","tid":1703572,"uid":161105,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-11-10T10:48:54.000Z","msg":"條友屌示威者<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-10T10:56:07.000Z","msg":"有冇圖"},{"pid":"4aae3bc5083aa13acabf2c98d558bd627f9571f9","tid":1703572,"uid":103842,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"52406be781b8cbee8aae53476536b32df76f3144","tid":1703572,"uid":161105,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-11-10T10:48:54.000Z","msg":"條友屌示威者<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-11-10T10:57:30.000Z","msg":"如果係真既話叫佢返大陸做雞啦"},{"pid":"1e5440c29a75d45ef7c36f4274eb531fd7537c84","tid":1703572,"uid":470,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"4aae3bc5083aa13acabf2c98d558bd627f9571f9","tid":1703572,"uid":103842,"like":1,"dislike":0,"scor